title: MS. PAT

description:
Ms. Pat is the guest and talks about fish hooking, getting choked, Elsa porn, and her new comedy THE MS. PAT SHOW premieres August 12th on BET+.  Also, a very special iGuest helps Whitney read ads.  Ms. Pat’s podcast THE PATDOWN comes out every Tuesday and her website is https://mspatcomedy.com/
